          "_name": "article02",
          "_sourceTheme": "startm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"start article2\" group=\"Article\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{\n    'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen,\n    'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n\t<mbr-parameters>\n\t\t<header>Size</header>\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Screen\" name=\"fullScreen\">\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n\t\t<input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"3\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n\t\t<input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"3\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n\t\t<input type=\"range\" inline name=\"imageWidth\" title=\"Image\" min=\"4\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\">\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Reverse\" name=\"reverseContent\">\n\t\t<header>Show/Hide</header>\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\" checked>\n\t\t<header>Background</header>\n\t\t<fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n\t\t\t<input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\">\n\t\t\t<input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#f8f5f2\" selected>\n\t\t\t<input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n\t\t</fieldset>\n\t\t<header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n\t\t<input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n\t\t<input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n\t\t<input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.8\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n\t</mbr-parameters>\n\n\t<div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n\t<div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\" opacity=\"{{overlayOpacity}}\" bg-color=\"{{overlayColor}}\"></div>\n\n\t<div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n\t\t<div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"col-12 col-md-12 col-lg-{{imageWidth}} image-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t<img class=\"w-100\" src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/generatedimage.png\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\">\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"col-12 col-md-12 col-lg\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"text-wrapper align-left\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h1 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\"><b>Mentora Gabriela Rodrigues</b></h1>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"mbr-text align-left mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">Especialista em estratégias de milhas para pessoas comuns que desejam viajar mais gastando muito menos.<br><br>Já ajudou dezenas de casais a organizarem viagens completas, inclusive lua de mel, com uma didática simples e um método claro.<br><br>Ela ensina exatamente o que funciona para transformar a lua de mel em uma viagem muito mais barata sem depender de sorte, ofertas ou longas pesquisas.</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" class=\"mbr-section-btn align-left mt-3\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\"><a class=\"btn btn-danger\" href=\"https://pay.hotmart.com/B99116111N?bid=1765196783917\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\" target=\"_blank\">QUERO APRENDER AGORA</a></div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n</section>",
